        <Parent_String>reporters (news) [300025508], journalists [300025501], people in communications [300103043], people in social science-related occupations [300168393], people in the social sciences and related occupations [300168333], people by occupation [300024980], people (agents) [300024979], People (hierarchy name) [300024978], Agents Facet [300264089]</Parent_String>
